{"type":null,"faqId":9662,"title":"荣耀 X1 （7D-501u）7.0  如何开启或关闭重力感应？","answer":"<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>您可以通过如下两种方式开启或关闭重力感应：</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;font-size:8pt;\"><span>l<span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>向下滑动状态栏，打开通知面板。点击自动旋转图标即可快速开启或关闭重力感应。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span></span></span>&nbsp;\n</p>\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=30138\" /> \n<p>\n\t&nbsp;\n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;font-size:8pt;\"><span>l<span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">在主屏幕上点击<b>设置</b></span><span> &gt; </span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">全部设置</span></b><span> &gt; </span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">辅助功能</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，勾选或清除<b>自动旋转屏幕</b>复选框，也可开启或关闭重力感应功能。</span></span> \n</p>\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=30140\" /> \n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span></span></span>&nbsp;\n</p>","faqTypeId":166,"faqType":"显示与外观","useful":2,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"266","faqTypeCode":"Tablet-Screen-Display","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1396259765000,"seriesProductName":"7D-501u","visitedTimes":161,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}